  imagemagick-6.1.3.2.ebuild:
  dont forget dev-perl/perlmagick needs to match these versions

  01 Nov 2004; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  imagemagick-6.0.7.1.ebuild, imagemagick-6.0.8.1.ebuild,
  imagemagick-6.1.0.1.ebuild, imagemagick-6.1.3.2.ebuild:
  Remove >=app-text/dgs-0.5.9.1 dep on USE=X because virtual/x11 provides all
  the same stuff, and they actually overwrite each other's files. Approved by
  sekretarz.

